msgid "Minesweeper-like Game"
msgstr "Minesweeperi moodi mäng"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kmines.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KMines is a classic Minesweeper game. The idea is to uncover all the squares "
"without blowing up any mines. When a mine is blown up, the game is over."
msgstr ""
"KMines on klassikaline Minesweeperi mäng. Selle siht on avada kõik ruudud, "
"ilma ühelgi miinil õhku lendamata. Kui miin plahvatab, on mäng läbi."
